cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI 

This paper is about improving the performance of collaborative filtering using neural interaction functions. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper proposes a new method for optimizing the performance of machine learning models. Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) concepts, as well as data science (cs.DS) and social and information networks (cs.SI) due to the nature of collaborative filtering.
